    "methodology": "EHE figures represent children known to local authorities as being electively home educated. The true figure is likely higher as there is no mandatory registration requirement in England. Registration rate represents the proportion of local authorities maintaining a voluntary register. SEND figures for home-educated children are based on ADCS annual surveys and DfE data linkage. Reasons for EHE are drawn from ADCS survey data where local authorities record the primary reason given at the point of deregistration.",
